snippet: Naomi O’Connell presented “Witches, Bitches & Women in Britches,” a program of songs in English, French and German, at Weill Recital Hall on Tuesday.
abstract: Vivien Schweitzer reviews performance by Irish mezzo-soprano Naomi O'Connell at Weill Recital Hall.
